461
00:44:04,800 --> 00:44:06,310
Si fakt zvláštny.

462
00:44:06,820 --> 00:44:09,510
Nikdy v živote som o niečom takomto nepočul.

463
00:44:10,260 --> 00:44:11,420
No, volá sa to „láskavosť“.

464
00:44:11,620 --> 00:44:13,040
Super, čo?

465
00:44:17,420 --> 00:44:18,420
Kde je?!

466
00:44:18,640 --> 00:44:19,840
Tvoja priateľka!

467
00:44:20,620 --> 00:44:22,200
Ukáž nám fotku.

468
00:44:38,150 --> 00:44:39,710
Počkajte.

469
00:44:48,460 --> 00:44:50,660
Ktorá je tvoja priateľka?

470
00:44:51,170 --> 00:44:52,710
Oboje.

471
00:44:52,930 --> 00:44:54,750
Bože!

472
00:44:54,750 --> 00:44:55,930
To je super!

473
